location.fullValue: Bordeaux Plan, Weavers Ridge Single Family

data.description: Almost New and Ready to Move Right In! This Gorgeous Island Breeze Floor Plan from Clayton Homes offers a Farmhouse Style Design with a Large 8' Kitchen Island, and Interior Barn Door Double Pantry The Kitchen, Dining and Family Room are Open for Entertaining. All Bedrooms have there own privacy, with the Primary Bedroom separated from the other two guest bedrooms. The Primary Bath offers a beautiful soaking tub, built in shelves, double vanity plus a large walk-in Shower. Secondary Bath also features Double Vanity with a Walk in Tub/Shower. Large laundry Room, Private Lot with Fenced Backyard. Great Location! Enjoy the peace and quiet of this Country setting.
